01:03:18,561 --> 01:03:19,994
My mother calls me
the night before and she goes,

1409
01:03:20,229 --> 01:03:21,355
'Do you die today
in the movie?. '

1410
01:03:21,798 --> 01:03:23,459
I go, 'Yeah.'

1411
01:03:23,900 --> 01:03:25,390
She goes, 'Why are they
save that to the very end?.

1412
01:03:25,835 --> 01:03:26,927
Is this a snuff movie?.
