02:00:51,477 --> 02:00:53,809
Corey walked in there,
and he was so alive,

2795
02:00:54,247 --> 02:00:58,479
and so friendly and he and l,
just we clicked.

2796
02:00:58,718 --> 02:01:01,243
I went, I did my audition
and then at the end of it,

