02:01:20,840 --> 02:01:24,606
And I went, "Give me a machete.
Let's give it a shot." (Laughs)

2806
02:01:24,844 --> 02:01:26,539
And I think that was
the end of it.

2807
02:01:26,779 --> 02:01:29,839
You could see with Corey.
You really could.

2808
02:01:30,283 --> 02:01:31,545
This young man
was going to skyrocket.

2809
02:01:31,784 --> 02:01:33,752
And I remember
it was a very big deal

