02:01:33,986 --> 02:01:34,975
because "Gremlins" and "Friday"
were both coming out

2811
02:01:35,421 --> 02:01:37,412
pretty much
over the same summer,

2812
02:01:37,657 --> 02:01:38,487
within a couple weeks
of each other

