2825
02:02:10,523 --> 02:02:13,583
And I do remember her doing
a lot of, kind of,

2826
02:02:13,826 --> 02:02:15,817
Iooking after me, making sure
that I was taken care of.

2827
02:02:16,062 --> 02:02:18,053
She was kind of the person

2828
02:02:18,497 --> 02:02:19,964
that I think I could probably
relate to most.

2829
02:02:20,399 --> 02:02:22,390
I at least felt that it was
a real connection.

2830
02:02:22,635 --> 02:02:24,762
As much as I could bring
to that role,

2831
02:02:25,004 --> 02:02:26,835
I wanted to bring to it.

2832
02:02:27,073 --> 02:02:28,973
There was thought about making

