02:02:32,878 --> 02:02:37,042
So Trish isn't really
one of the guys.

2835
02:02:37,483 --> 02:02:38,973
She's an outsider.

2836
02:02:39,418 --> 02:02:40,851
She's not ready to become
part of the party,

2837
02:02:41,087 --> 02:02:42,384
or the party doesn't want her.

2838
02:02:42,621 --> 02:02:44,418
Tommy's an outsider,
like Jason.

2839
02:02:44,657 --> 02:02:46,591
Tommy's a kid
that doesn't fit in.

2840
02:02:46,826 --> 02:02:48,589
I argue that one of the reasons
Tommy Jarvis

2841
02:02:48,828 --> 02:02:50,090
has been as popular as he's been

2842
02:02:50,529 --> 02:02:52,724
is because that was a very
relatable character

2843
02:02:52,965 --> 02:02:54,762
to the core audience
in these movies

2844
02:02:55,000 --> 02:02:57,594
