to the old formula.

4334
03:05:17,473 --> 03:05:20,499
Obviously, 5, where you have
an imitation Jason,

4335
03:05:20,742 --> 03:05:23,074
angered the fans.

4336
03:05:23,312 --> 03:05:24,404
